cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DC, cs.NE 

This paper is about benchmarking deep learning software tools, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also focuses on the performance of these tools when training neural networks for computer vision tasks (cs.CV) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the optimization of running performance, which is related to neural engineering (cs.NE).
